Path: Nushell
Content:
tiffany352 added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3132] optional exit codes to the 
``exit``
 command
fdncred improved the 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3133] coercion with $nothing for comparisons
, cleaned up 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3137] some warnings
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3144] moved bel and backspace to 
``char``
, switched 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3154] surf to use the hyper-client
rezural refactored 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3135] the internal draw_table functionality to output strings
, updated 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3136] minus (the paging support crate) to 3.3.0
ahkrr fixed some 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3140] locking logic with output
, fixed a 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3159] unicode character counting issue
tw4452852 fixed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3146] trash functionality
jonathandturner released 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3149] 0.28
, fixed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3153] input streams of text larger than a buffer
